sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Astro (RTL)
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant G as Gemini
    participant AA as analysis_agent
    participant RA as rag_agent
    participant C as ChromaDB
    participant J as Jira KAN

    U->>UI: transcript / audio / sample meeting
    opt audio file or recording
        UI->>API: POST /api/transcribe
        API->>G: Gemini audio → text
        API-->>UI: transcript
    end
    UI->>API: POST /api/meetings
    API->>API: parse + chunk + embed
    API->>C: index chunks
    API->>AA: run(transcript)
    AA-->>UI: summary + tasks (SSR)
    U->>UI: RAG question
    UI->>API: POST /ask
    API->>C: query by meeting_id
    API->>RA: context + question
    RA-->>UI: natural answer + footnote
    U->>UI: confirm task
    UI->>API: POST /jira/create
    API->>J: new issue